<h2>Industry-Specific AI Overview Statistics</h2>
<p><strong>34. Healthcare queries trigger AI Overviews 88% of the time.</strong>
(Source: Digital Applied / ALM Corp, 2026)
The highest AI Overview rate of any industry category.</p>
<p><strong>35. Education queries trigger AI Overviews 83% of the time.</strong>
(Source: Digital Applied, 2026)
Second only to healthcare in AI Overview prevalence.</p>
<p><strong>36. B2B Technology queries trigger AI Overviews 82% of the time.</strong>
(Source: Digital Applied, 2026)
Technology and SaaS companies face among the highest exposure to AI Overviews.</p>
<p><strong>37. Restaurant queries trigger AI Overviews 78% of the time.</strong>
(Source: Digital Applied, 2026)
<a href="/blog/local-seo-guide/">Local business searches</a> are heavily affected by AI Overview expansion.</p>
<p><strong>38. Insurance queries trigger AI Overviews 63% of the time.</strong>
(Source: Digital Applied, 2026)
Financial services categories see moderate to high AI Overview rates.</p>
<p><strong>39. Entertainment queries trigger AI Overviews 37% of the time.</strong>
(Source: Digital Applied, 2026)
The lowest rate among the 9 tracked industries. Entertainment queries are more navigational.</p>
<p><img loading="lazy" alt="Top cited domains in Google AI Overviews including YouTube Quora Reddit and Wikipedia" src="/images/blog/google-ai-overview-top-cited-domains.webp" /></p>
<h2>AI Search Market and Growth Statistics</h2>
<p><strong>40. AI search activity equals 56% of global search usage.</strong>
(Source: SparkToro / BrightEdge, 2026)
When combining all AI search tools, AI-assisted search accounts for more than half of global search volume.</p>
<p><strong>41. ChatGPT leads AI search market share at 60.7%.</strong>
(Source: Sedestral, January 2026)
Followed by Google Gemini at 15.0% and Microsoft Copilot at 13.2%.</p>
<p><strong>42. ChatGPT drives 87.4% of all AI referral traffic to websites.</strong>
(Source: <a href="/blog/ai-search-referral-traffic-stats/">Multiple sources</a>, 2026)
Despite Google AI Overviews reaching more users, ChatGPT sends far more referral traffic.</p>
<p><strong>43. AI referral traffic accounts for 1.08% of all website traffic.</strong>
(Source: Multiple analytics studies, 2026)
Growing at roughly 1% month over month. Small but accelerating.</p>
<p><strong>44. 810 million people use ChatGPT daily as of early 2026.</strong>
(Source: OpenAI, 2026)
ChatGPT has over 900 million weekly active users globally.</p>
<h2>What These Google AI Overview Statistics Mean for SEO</h2>
<p><strong>45. CTRs for high-funnel queries will be 20-30% lower through 2026.</strong>
(Source: Seer Interactive projection, 2025)
Based on the current 6-month decline rate continuing through the year.</p>
<p><strong>46. Pages not updated quarterly are 3x more likely to lose AI citations.</strong>
(Source: Semrush, 2025)
Content freshness directly affects whether AI Overviews cite your pages.</p>
<p><strong>47. Domain authority is the number 1 predictor of AI citations.</strong>
(Source: SE Ranking, 2025)
High-traffic sites earn 3x more AI citations than low-traffic sites.</p>
<p><strong>48. Brands with profiles on review platforms have 3x higher citation chances.</strong>
(Source: Multiple studies, 2025)
Profiles on Trustpilot, G2, Capterra, and similar platforms increase AI citation probability.</p>
